Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.57,0:15:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道这附近有没有哪家店的茶比较好喝的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 有一家店不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 请务必带我去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.68,0:16:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:11.75,miao,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(163,82)\fs24\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270}想着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:11.75,miao,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(105,155)\fs24\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270}他是从哪里来的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬社长 走…吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这身奇怪的打扮是要干嘛啊…亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:27.73,miao,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(501,99)\fs24\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270}真实身份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:27.73,miao,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(437,160)\fs24\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270}果然是绝不可以泄漏的
