Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧吧？亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:18:02.03,miao,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(542,140)\fs25\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270}我并不是你所说
