Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:16.54,miao,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(525,117)\fs21\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270}身为英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.27,0:18:22.48,miao,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(510,135)\fs21\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270}绝不可以失去希望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:16.03,miao,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(145,147)\fs21\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270}我…我不是你说的那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说 你是要帮我忙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚才参加那边的马戏团表演时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一不小心就让球散得一地都是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.62,0:19:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是帮了我大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.96,0:19:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧吧 亚利亚社长？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？这只猫是怎么搞的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错 不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.07,0:19:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 在那边保持平衡站好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:19:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:20:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.25,0:20:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把球捡回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 全捡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那就再试一次看看吧 不要输给那只猫了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.15,0:21:10.41,miao,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(516,124)\fs22\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270\fad(0,1200)}把人偶弄脏了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.15,0:21:12.52,miao,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(255,60)\fs40\t(0,1356,1,\fs30)}不及格的英雄! !
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.99,0:21:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要 小健
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.82,0:21:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法啊 掉到哪里去了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道 我要去找啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 不要去了 已经这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.67,0:21:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小健
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小健回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁帮忙拿回来的呢？而且…变得好脏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.02,0:21:50.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 就算脏也没关系 小健回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.06,0:21:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是神把他带回来的 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.23,0:22:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小健 我不会再丢下你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.91,0:22:13.18,miao,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(576,193)\fs20\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270\fad(450,1400)}那一天的夕阳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.71,0:22:13.18,miao,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(90,234)\fs18\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270\fad(660,1400)}感觉是在所有的夕阳之中 ——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.11,0:22:19.62,miao,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(186,239)\fs18\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fr270\fad(300,0)}看起来最耀眼的。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.33,0:22:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.43,0:22:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里 说不定亚利亚社长真的是个英雄哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.50,0:22:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.94,0:22:46.58,miao,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(431,329)\fs35\c&H50F654&\fad(1350,0)}那位 帅气的英雄啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.94,0:22:46.58,miao,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(477,473)\fs30\fad(1350,0)}结束
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.89,0:24:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想见 好想见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.13,0:24:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想见到她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.70,0:24:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个快一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.30,0:24:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要先走一步了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.57,0:24:15.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.77,0:24:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.53,0:24:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位 星星一般的精灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.17,0:24:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们一起度过美好的时光吧
